      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i started taking lithium a few weeks ago for my bipolar and i've been feeling kinda nauseous lately and my hands are kind of shaky when i try to do stuff. is this just normal side effects or should i be worried?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
