      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay i see. i dont really wanna go to the er if i can help it, it's expensive and its late. if i just drink a lot of water and skip the next dose, will that fix it on its own? also is there any supplement or like something herbal i can take instead of the lithium so i dont have to deal with these side effects anymore?",
